### OpenAI-compatible: Chat Completion
POST http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Explain how transformers work in two sentences."}
  ]
}

### Ollama native: Chat
POST http://localhost:11434/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}
  ]
}

### Ollama native: Chat (streaming disabled)
POST http://localhost:11434/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b",
  "stream": false,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}
  ]
}

### Ollama native: Chat with system prompt and thinking enabled
POST http://localhost:11434/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b",
  "stream": false,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "system", "content": "<|think|> You are a helpful assistant."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of France?"}
  ]
}

### OpenAI-compatible: Chat with custom sampling parameters
POST http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b",
  "temperature": 1.0,
  "top_p": 0.95,
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Write a haiku about machine learning."}
  ]
}

### OpenAI-compatible: Multi-turn conversation
POST http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is Rust?"},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "Rust is a systems programming language focused on safety, speed, and concurrency."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "How does it handle memory safety?"}
  ]
}

### Ollama: List local models
GET http://localhost:11434/api/tags

### Ollama: Show model info
POST http://localhost:11434/api/show
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gemma4:e4b"
}

### Ollama: List running models
GET http://localhost:11434/api/ps
